OL,3,CMonthly antisemitic hate crimes
OL,4,Crecorded by Met Police hit two-year
OL,5,Chigh
OL,7,FThe number of antisemitic hate crimes
OL,8,Frecorded last month by the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police in London was the
OL,10,Fhighest in two years.
OL,12,FSome 140 offences were logged across
OL,13,Fthe capital in April, up from 98 in
OL,14,FMarch and 67 in February, according to
OL,15,Fnew data published by the force.
OL,17,FThe borough of Barnet saw the highest
OL,18,Fnumber, accounting for 51 of the 140,
OL,19,For 36%.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
