OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778069461
OL,3,CMonthly antisemitic hate crimes
OL,4,Crecorded by Met Police hit two-year
OL,5,Chigh
OL,7,FBarnet includes the districts of
OL,8,FGolders Green, Hendon and Finchley,
OL,9,Fall of which have large Jewish
OL,10,Fpopulations, where a string of
OL,11,Fapparent antisemitic attacks took
OL,12,Fplace last month.
OL,14,FAttempted arson attacks were carried
OL,15,Fout at Finchley Reform Synagogue on
OL,16,FApril 15, at the building of a former
OL,17,FJewish charity in Hendon on April 18,
OL,18,Fand at a memorial wall in Golders
OL,19,FGreen on April 28.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778069461
OL,3,CMonthly antisemitic hate crimes
OL,4,Crecorded by Met Police hit two-year
OL,5,Chigh
OL,7,FGolders Green was also the scene of a
OL,8,Fdouble stabbing on April 29 that is
OL,9,Fbeing treated as an act of terrorism.
OL,11,FThe borough of Camden, to the south of
OL,12,FBarnet, saw 17 antisemitic offences
OL,13,Frecorded by the Met Police in April,
OL,14,Falong with 16 in Hackney, 10 in
OL,15,FHaringey and seven in Westminster.
OL,17,FOverall, 21 of the 32 London boroughs
OL,18,Fsaw at least one antisemitic hate
OL,19,Fcrime logged by the Met Police last
OL,20,Fmonth.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
