CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778069461
OL,3,CMonthly antisemitic hate crimes
OL,4,Crecorded by Met Police hit two-year
OL,5,Chigh
OL,7,FThe 140 offences recorded in April is
OL,8,Fthe highest monthly figure since the
OL,9,Fforce changed the way it counts hate
OL,10,Fcrime in March 2024
OL,12,FData from before March 2024, under the
OL,13,Fprevious method of counting, showed a
OL,14,Flarge spike in antisemitic hate crimes
OL,15,Fin London following the outbreak of
OL,16,Fthe Hamas-Israel conflict in October
OL,17,F2023
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
