PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778069461
OL,3,CMonthly antisemitic hate crimes
OL,4,Crecorded by Met Police hit two-year
OL,5,Chigh
OL,7,FOffences jumped from 61 in September
OL,8,F2023 to 518 in October, with 411 in
OL,9,FNovember, 228 in December, 198 in
OL,10,FJanuary 2024 and 174 in February
OL,12,FThe figures come as the Met Police
OL,13,Fannounced it was creating a community
OL,14,Fprotection team of 100 extra officers
OL,15,Fto provide a "more visible,
OL,16,Fintelligence-led and co-ordinated
OL,17,Fpresence focused on protecting Jewish
OL,18,Fcommunities across London."
OL,26,@wD@NOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
