FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1778069461
OL,3,CMonthly antisemitic hate crimes
OL,4,Crecorded by Met Police hit two-year
OL,5,Chigh
OL,7,FThe new team will involve
OL,8,Fneighbourhood policing as well as
OL,9,Fspecialist protection and counter-
OL,10,Fterrorism capabilities, and marks the
OL,11,F"beginning of a new, more sustainable
OL,12,Fand consistent model of protection
OL,13,Fbuilt around local knowledge,
OL,14,Fvisibility and partnership, rather
OL,15,Fthan relying solely on repeated short-
OL,16,Fterm surges".
OL,18,FThe Jewish community "faces some of
OL,19,Fthe highest levels of hate crime
OL,20,Falongside significant terrorist and
OL,21,Fhostile state threats," the Met added.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@LO]zD@VOU}D@WO]
